##Terraform: 
Its a open source tool for infrastructure provisioning & Deploying Application
Working on the principle of IaC
Automate and manage your infrastructure and services that run on the platform

##Architecture:
1. Provider : Allow us to communicate with specific set of APIs
provider "aws" {
  region = " "
  access_key = " "
  secret_key = " "
  }
2. Core
Tf-Config - What needs to create and configure
Tf-State - Up to date state of the current setup
